    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously preserved to look and drive like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no dents, scratches, or stone chips to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the upholstery shows no wear, and every electronic feature and accessory functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been kept in a climate-controlled environment with a comprehensive service history. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or a discerning buyer to own an example of this model in showroom-perfect state.",
