      "description": "Ready for a rewarding restoration project? This vehicle is looking for a dedicated new owner to bring it back to its best! It is currently in poor condition and will need significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, making it the perfect canvas for a car enthusiast or hobbyist. Grab this opportunity to rebuild a classic to your own specifications at a great price!",
